y' => 'Betaalbestellingsopsomming','Display widgets inside the order summary at the checkout page.' => 'Vertoon widgets binne die bestelopsomming by die betaalbladsy.','Checkout Below Place Order' => 'Betaal onder Plaas bestelling','Display widgets below the place order button at the checkout page.' => 'Vertoon widgets onder die plaasbestelknoppie by die betaalbladsy.','Checkout Footer' => 'Checkout-voetskrif','Display widgets on the checkout footer. Only displayed if using the plugin\'s checkout footer.' => 'Vertoon widgets op die betaalpuntvoetskrif. Word slegs vertoon as die inprop se betaalvoetskrif gebruik word.','Classic' => 'Klassiek','Boxed' => 'Geboks','Split' => 'Verdeel','Minimalist' => 'Minimalisties','Fluid Checkout and Delivery Date plugins by CodeRockz' => 'Fluid Checkout en Delivery Date plugins deur CodeRockz','<p>We detected that you are using the plugins Delivery & Pickup Date Time for WooCommerce (free and PRO) by CodeRockz. Integration with these plugins have been moved to Fluid Checkout PRO.</p>' => '<p>Ons het bespeur dat jy die inproppe Delivery &amp; Pickup Date Time vir WooCommerce (gratis en PRO) deur CodeRockz gebruik. Integrasie met hierdie inproppe is na Fluid Checkout PRO geskuif.</p>','Upgrade to PRO' => 'Gradeer op na PRO','Fluid Checkout database updated successfully' => 'Fluid Checkout-databasis is suksesvol opgedateer','The database changes where applied successfully.' => 'Die databasis verander waar suksesvol toegepas.','Ok' => 'Goed','Dismiss' => 'Verwerp','Fluid Checkout database update' => 'Fluid Checkout-databasisopdatering','Some changes to the database are required. As with any update, we recommend you to <strong>take a full backup of your website before proceeding</strong>.' => 'Sommige veranderinge aan die databasis word vereis. Soos met enige opdatering, beveel ons aan dat u <strong>&#39;n volledige rugsteun van u webwerf neem voordat u verder gaan</strong> .','Update database' => 'Dateer databasis op','Fluid Checkout is not compatible with the Divi Builder checkout layout' => 'Fluid Checkout is nie versoenbaar met die Divi Builder-betaaluitleg nie','<p>Fluid Checkout needs the classic WooCommerce shortcode-based checkout form to work. When using the Divi Builder to customize the look and feel of the checkout page, the classic shortcodes are replaced with custom widgets from the Divi Builder for each part of the checkout page. These custom widgets are not compatible with Fluid Checkout.</p><p>Please edit your checkout page replacing the Divi Builder widgets with the a text widget containing the shortcode <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code>.</p>' => '<p>Fluid Checkout benodig die klassieke WooCommerce-kortkode-gebaseerde betaalvorm om te werk. Wanneer die Divi Builder gebruik word om die voorkoms en gevoel van die betaalbladsy aan te pas, word die klassieke kortkodes vervang met pasgemaakte legstukke van die Divi Builder vir elke deel van die betaalbladsy. Hierdie pasgemaakte legstukke is nie versoenbaar met Fluid Checkout nie.</p><p> Redigeer asseblief jou betaalbladsy en vervang die Divi Builder-legstukke met &#39;n tekslegstuk wat die kortkode <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code> bevat.</p>','Edit the checkout page' => 'Wysig die betaalbladsy','Read the documentation.' => 'Lees die dokumentasie.','Germanized PRO multistep checkout feature needs to be disabled when using Fluid Checkout' => 'Geremaniseerde PRO meerstap-afhandeling-funksie moet gedeaktiveer word wanneer Fluid Checkout gebruik word','When using Fluid Checkout, the multistep feature from the Germanized PRO plugin becomes unnecessary and can cause <strong>critical errors while processing new orders</strong>. Please disable the Germanized PRO multistep checkout feature in the plugin settings.' => 'Wanneer Fluid Checkout gebruik word, word die meerstap-kenmerk van die Germanized PRO-inprop onnodig en kan dit <strong>kritieke foute veroorsaak tydens die verwerking van nuwe bestellings</strong> . Deaktiveer asseblief die Geremaniseerde PRO multistap-afhandeling-funksie in die inpropinstellings.','Go to Germanized settings' => 'Gaan na germaniseerde instellings','Thanks for choosing Fluid Checkout!' => 'Dankie dat jy Fluid Checkout gekies het!','You have been using the plugin for a while now. How do you like it so far? <br>Please give us a quick rating, we appreciate every bit of feedback and it encourages us to keep improving the plugin :)' => 'Jy gebruik die inprop nou al &#39;n rukkie. Hoe hou jy daarvan tot dusver?<br> Gee ons asseblief &#39;n vinnige gradering, ons waardeer elke bietjie terugvoer en dit moedig ons aan om aan te hou om die inprop te verbeter :)','Rate the plugin' => 'Beoordeel die inprop','I need help!' => 'Ek het hulp nodig!','The plugin WooCommerce Checkout Manager by Quadlayers is not compatibile with Fluid Checkout' => 'Die inprop WooCommerce Checkout Manager deur Quadlayers is nie versoenbaar met Fluid Checkout nie','Some features of WooCommerce Checkout Manager by Quadlayers might not work as expected when using it with Fluid Checkout. Read <a href="%s">our documentation</a> for more information and alternative solutions.' => 'Sommige kenmerke van WooCommerce Checkout Manager deur Quadlayers sal dalk nie werk soos verwag wanneer dit met Fluid Checkout gebruik word nie. Lees <a href="%s">ons dokumentasie</a> vir meer inligting en alternatiewe oplossings.','Read documentation' => 'Lees dokumentasie','Don\'t show this again' => 'Moenie dit weer wys nie','Special offers' => 'Spesiale aanbiedinge','Extend all the goodness of Fluid Checkout to your cart page and thank you pages.' => 'Brei al die goedheid van Fluid Checkout uit na jou mandjie-bladsy en dankie-bladsye.','Fluid Checkout PRO' => 'Fluid Checkout PRO','Design templates, optimized cart and order received pages, account matching, and much more.' => 'Ontwerp sjablone, geoptimaliseerde mandjie en bestelling ontvang bladsye, rekeningpassing, en nog baie meer.','The best tools to further <strong>improve your WooCommerce checkout conversion rate</strong> and make the purchase experience consistent on the entire journey.' => 'Die beste hulpmiddels om <strong>u WooCommerce-afhandelingsomskakelingskoers verder te verbeter</strong> en die aankoopervaring konsekwent te maak op die hele reis.','More design templates' => 'Meer ontwerpsjablone','Optimized cart page' => 'Geoptimaliseerde mandjie bladsy','Optimized order received / thank you page' => 'Geoptimaliseerde bestelling ontvang / dankie bladsy','Edit cart contents at checkout page' => 'Wysig inhoud van die mandjie by die betaalbladsy','Account matching / user matching' => 'Rekeningpassing / gebruikerpassing','Express Checkout buttons from supported payment methods' => 'Express Checkout-knoppies vanaf ondersteunde betaalmetodes','Trust symbols on the cart and thank you pages' => 'Vertrou simbole op die kar en dankie-bladsye','More positions for the coupon code on the checkout page' => 'Meer posisies vir die koeponkode op die betaalbladsy','Integrated coupon code field on the cart page' => 'Ge√Øntegreerde koeponkode veld op die mandjie bladsy','International phone numbers' => 'Internasionale telefoonnommers','Gift messages and packing slips' => 'Geskenkboodskappe en pakstrokies','Local pickup and in-store collection' => 'Plaaslike afhaal en afhaal in die winkel','Upgrade to PRO &mdash; 99 EUR' => 'Gradeer op na PRO - 99 EUR','Fluid Checkout PRO ‚Äì Bundle' => 'Fluid Checkout PRO ‚Äì Bundel','All PRO features + All add-ons for a special price.' => 'Alle PRO-kenmerke + Alle byvoegings vir &#39;n spesiale prys.','The bundle includes all add-ons we currently offer and Fluid Checkout add-ons we launch in the future.' => 'Die bondel bevat alle byvoegings wat ons tans bied en Fluid Checkout-byvoegings wat ons in die toekoms bekendstel.','226 EUR value (Save 42%)' => '226 EUR waarde (Spaar 42%)','Google Address Autocomplete' => 'Google-adres outovoltooi','Address Book' => 'Adresboek','EU-VAT Assistant' => 'EU-BTW-assistent','All future add-ons *' => 'Alle toekomstige byvoegings *','* For as long as you have an active subscription.' => '* Solank jy &#39;n aktiewe intekening het.','Get the Bundle ‚Äì Only 129 EUR' => 'Kry die bondel ‚Äì Slegs 129 EUR','All prices shown in EUR. If there are any divergencies with the prices on our website, the offers shown on the website superseed these and will be applied.' => 'Alle pryse in EUR. As daar enige afwykings met die pryse op ons webwerf is, vervang die aanbiedinge wat op die webwerf gewys word dit en sal dit toegepas word.','Add-ons' => 'Byvoegings','Enhance your checkout experience with these add-ons.' => 'Verbeter jou betaalervaring met hierdie byvoegings.','I already have it ‚Äì Hide this offer' => 'Ek het dit reeds ‚Äì Versteek hierdie aanbod','Installed &mdash; Activate' => 'Ge√Ønstalleer ‚Äî Aktiveer','Activated' => 'Geaktiveer','Up to 40% less checkout fields to fill in.' => 'Tot 40% minder betaalpuntvelde om in te vul.','Avoid delivery delays and unsatisfied customers. Collect the <strong>correct address information</strong> from the first time they buy with you.' => 'Vermy afleweringsvertragings en ontevrede kli√´nte. Versamel die <strong>korrekte adresinligting</strong> vanaf die eerste keer dat hulle by jou koop.','Get this add-on &mdash; 29 EUR' => 'Kry hierdie byvoeging - 29 EUR','Address book' => 'Adresboek','Multiple saved addresses for shipping and billing.' => 'Veelvuldige gestoorde adresse vir versending en fakturering.','Let customers <strong>save multiple shipping and billing addresses</strong> on their account and choose which ones to use at checkout and cart pages.' => 'Laat klante <strong>verskeie aflewerings- en faktuuradresse op hul rekening stoor</strong> en kies watter hulle by betaalpunt- en mandjiebladsye moet gebruik.','Get this add-on &mdash; 59 EUR' => 'Kry hierdie byvoeging - 59 EUR','Simplified EU-VAT validation for your store.' => 'Vereenvoudigde EU-BTW-bekragtiging vir jou winkel.','Collect and <strong>validate EU VAT numbers at the checkout page</strong>, removes tax charges on reverse charge basis and confirms customer location when needed.' => 'Versamel en <strong>bekragtig EU-BTW-nommers by die betaalpuntbladsy</strong> , verwyder belastingheffings op omgekeerde heffingsgrondslag en bevestig kli√´ntligging wanneer nodig.','Get this add-on &mdash; 39 EUR' => 'Kry hierdie byvoeging - 39 EUR','All add-ons are sold separately and require the <strong>Fluid Checkout Lite</strong> plugin to be installed and activated, except when noted.' => 'Alle byvoegings word afsonderlik verkoop en vereis dat die <strong>Fluid Checkout Lite-</strong> inprop ge√Ønstalleer en geaktiveer word, behalwe wanneer dit opgemerk word.','Select an image' => 'Kies &#39;n prent','No image selected.' => 'Geen prent gekies nie.','Remove image' => 'Verwyder prent','<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Log in to your account</a> to get your license key, or <a href="%s" target="_blank">purchase a new license key</a>.' => '<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Meld by jou rekening aan</a> om jou lisensiesleutel te kry, of <a href="%s" target="_blank">koop &#39;n nuwe lisensiesleutel</a> .','Valid until %s.' => 'Geldig tot %s.','Expired on %s.' => 'Verval op %s.','<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Log in to your account</a> to renew your license key and continue to receive updates and support.' => '<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Meld by jou rekening aan</a> om jou lisensiesleutel te hernu en gaan voort om opdaterings en ondersteuning te ontvang.','License key cancelled.' => 'Lisensiesleutel gekanselleer.','<a href="%s" target="_blank">Purchase a new license key</a> and continue to receive updates and support.' => '<a href="%s" target="_blank">Koop &#39;n nuwe lisensiesleutel</a> en gaan voort om opdaterings en ondersteuning te ontvang.','Error: ' => 'Fout: ','Setup & Documentation' => 'Opstelling en dokumentasi